=== Transportation ===
* {{ill|lt=Gifu Shared Car|Q5560101|qid=Q5560101|lt=Gifu Bus|1=Gifu Bus}} Get off at Ozaki Danchi Line "Sohara" {{ill|lt=Bus Stop|Q953806|qid=Q953806|lt=Bus Stop|1=Bus stop}} and walk for about 10 minutes.
** {{ill|lt=JR Gifu Station Bus Terminal|Q11226229|qid=Q11226229|1=JR Gifu Station Bus Terminal}} Platform 13 "Suwayama Danchi" "{{ill|lt=Gifu Prefectural Kakamigahara High School|Q11471490|qid=Q11471490|lt=Kakamigahara High School|1=Gifu Prefectural Kakamihara Senior High School}}" "{{ill|lt=Techno Plaza (Gifu Prefecture)|Q11319203|qid=Q11319203|lt=Techno Plaza|1=Techno Plaza}}" and "{{ill|lt=Mikakino Station|Q6845663|qid=Q6845663|1=Mikakino Station}}".
** {{ill|lt=Meitetsu Gifu Bus Stop|Q11415771|qid=Q11415771|1=Meitetsu Gifu Bus Stop}} Take the bus bound for ``Suwayama Danchi,'' ``Kakamigahara High School,'' ``Techno Plaza,'' and ``Mikakino Station'' at bus stop 6.
* {{ill|lt=Kakamigahara City Fureai Bus|Q11412316|qid=Q11412316|1=Kakamigahara City Fureai Bus}}
** Get off at Sohara Line "Sohara Furuichibacho" bus stop and walk for about 8 minutes.

